                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8667" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2175</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1400 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“新绿”到“长青”还有多远——赣锋锂业ESG“赶考”之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How Far From &quot;New Green&quot; to &quot;Everlasting Green&quot; ——The Way of &quot;Catching up the Examination&quot; of ESG in Ganfeng Lithium</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周俊卿，郑珑，易彩云，蓝黄娴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西赣锋锂业集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赣锋锂业；ESG 战略；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ganfeng Lithium; ESG Strategy; Sustainable Development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在当前倡导绿色低碳、追求高质量发展的时代背景下，企业积极进行ESG实践显得尤为重要，它将助力企业可持续发展，实现社会效益和经济效益有机统一。本案例通过分析赣锋锂业实施ESG战略的动因，以及在环境、社会和公司治理三个维度的具体举措和取得的成效，探寻企业如何借助ESG战略减轻企业风险、增强市场竞争力，并实现可持续发展的道路。基于本案例的学习，希望学生能够深刻理解ESG的内涵，掌握企业实施ESG战略的动因、措施及成效，深入思考ESG战略如何赋能企业可持续发展，实现社会效益和经济效益的双重提升，进而为推动全球绿色低碳发展贡献智慧与力量。同时，本案例也旨在对赣锋锂业ESG战略实践的解读，为其他同行业企业探索和践行ESG战略提供借鉴参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the current context of advocating green low-carbon and pursuing high-quality development, it is particularly important for enterprises to actively engage in ESG practices, which will help them develop sustainably and realize the organic unity of social and economic benefits. This case analyzes the motivation of Ganfeng Lithium&#39;s ESG strategy, as well as its specific initiatives and achievements in the three dimensions of environment, society and corporate governance, and explores how enterprises can mitigate corporate risks, enhance market competitiveness, and achieve sustainable development with the help of ESG strategy. Based on the study of this case, we hope that students can deeply understand the connotation of ESG, grasp the motivation, measures and effectiveness of the implementation of ESG strategy by enterprises, and think deeply about how ESG strategy empowers the sustainable development of enterprises, realizes the double enhancement of social and economic benefits, and then contributes to the promotion of the global green and low-carbon development with wisdom and strength. At the same time, this case also aims to interpret the ESG strategy practice of Ganfeng Lithium and provide reference for other enterprises in the same industry to explore and practice ESG strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《商业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG概念及驱动因素；利益相关者理论；价值共创理论；三重底线理论；战略性企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-09</td>
